@page
@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Akses Ditolak - Monitoring JIFAS</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, system-ui, sans-serif;
            background: #f0f2f5; min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }
        .card {
            background: white; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 48px 40px; text-align: center; max-width: 480px;
        }
        .icon {
            width: 64px; height: 64px; margin: 0 auto 24px;
            background: #fef2f2; border-radius: 50%; display: grid; place-items: center;
        }
        .icon svg { color: #b91c1c; width: 32px; height: 32px; }
        h1 { font-size: 24px; color: #1f2937; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        p { color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 32px; }
        a {
            display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #667eea;
            color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600; transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        a:hover { background: #5568d3; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="icon">
            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Akses Ditolak</h1>
        <p>Anda tidak memiliki izin untuk mengakses halaman ini. Dashboard monitoring hanya dapat diakses oleh administrator sistem dengan API Key yang valid.</p>
        <a href="/Admin/Login">Login dengan Admin API Key</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
